description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket will launch the Starlink (12-7) mission on Monday, January 27, 2025 at 8:22 PM (UTC).
An ISRO GSLV-II rocket will launch the NVS-02 (IRNSS-1K) mission on Wednesday, January 29, 2025 at 12:53 AM (UTC).
A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket will launch the SpainSat NG I mission on Thursday, January 30, 2025 at 1:34 AM (UTC).
A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket will launch the Starlink (12-3) mission. The launch date is currently targeted for January 30, 2025 (UTC).
A Gilmour Space Eris rocket will launch the Eris Debut Flight mission. The launch date is currently targeted for January, 2025 (UTC).
